OL,7,FThe family of a homeless man who died
OL,8,Fin a police cell after being arrested
OL,9,Fhave said they are still searching for
OL,10,Fanswers five years after his death.
OL,12,FSimeon Francis, 35, died in a cell at
OL,13,FTorquay Police Station on 20 May 2020
OL,14,Fafter being arrested in Exeter.
OL,16,FAt the start of an inquest into his
OL,17,Fdeath being held at County Hall in
OL,18,FExeter, senior coroner Ian Arrow read
OL,19,Fa statement from Simeon's sister,
OL,20,FAngie Hayward.
