OL,7,FShe said Simeon had been involved with
OL,8,Fdrugs and she had lost contact with
OL,9,Fhim in the final months of his life.
OL,11,F"The police came to my home and told
OL,12,Fme Simeon had died," Mrs Hayward said.
OL,14,F"Although it was a massive shock, due
OL,15,Fto his lifestyle I was not surprised.
OL,17,F"But when they told me he had died in
OL,18,Fpolice custody, I was very surprised
OL,19,Fand upset.
