OL,7,F"I know I speak for all of Simeon's
OL,8,Fextended family when I say I hope the
OL,9,Finquest gives us the answers as to how
OL,10,FSimeon came to die".
OL,12,FThe court heard that the cause of
OL,13,FSimeon's death was recorded as "sudden
OL,14,Funexpected death in epilepsy".
OL,16,FThe inquest continues.
